    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The day is almost over. We’re on deck chairs reading and writing and Jordan asks me to make dinner plans. I tell her that I just have a few questions for her to help me make my decision: “In a fight between Beyoncé and J-Lo, who would win? And why?” We both think that Jenny from the block would be win, but maybe Beyoncé’s bootie might be a wildcard. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "The day is almost over. We’re on deck chairs reading and writing and Jordan asks me to make dinner plans. I tell her that I just have a few questions for her to help me make my decision: “In a fight between Beyoncé and J-Lo, who would win? And why?” We both think that Jenny from the block would be win, but maybe Beyoncé’s bootie might be a wildcard. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
